// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1918 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 884f3818-4c32-5aa7-943e-9611b5c524c3

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*")
